{"id":236,"date":"2007-04-13T13:14:47","date_gmt":"2007-04-13T13:14:47","guid":{"rendered":"http://192.168.5.119/2.2/?p=236"},"modified":"2007-04-13T13:14:47","modified_gmt":"2007-04-13T13:14:47","slug":"%e6%8a%80%e5%b7%a7%ef%bc%9a%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e5%9c%a8thunderbird%e4%b8%ad%e6%9b%b4%e6%94%b9%e9%82%ae%e4%bb%b6%e6%a0%87%e9%a2%98","status":"publish","link":"https://xbeta.info/%e6%8a%80%e5%b7%a7%ef%bc%9a%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e5%9c%a8thunderbird%e4%b8%ad%e6%9b%b4%e6%94%b9%e9%82%ae%e4%bb%b6%e6%a0%87%e9%a2%98.htm","title":{"rendered":"技巧：如何在Thunderbird中更改邮件标题"},"content":{"rendered":"<div><a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/main/html/showpic.html#url=http://static15.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/46dac66f793f0007258be\" TARGET=\"_blank\"><img STYLE=\"FLOAT: left; MARGIN: 4px\" SRC=\"http://static15.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/46dac66f793f0007258be\" BORDER=\"0\"></a>Thunderbird或许不是最好的免费邮件客户端，但xbeta坚守之，并总结技巧。</p>\n<p><strong><br />\n需求</strong><br />\n　　收到标题为空的邮件，改成正确的标题<br />\n　　如果你有这种习惯：任务完成后，把邮件标题改为“已完成：xxx”<br />\n　　有些客户端可以直接修改，但Thunderbird要用扩展和一些技巧，如下<br />\n<b>方案</b><br />\n　　扩展 TB Header Tools Extension<br />\n　　主页 <a HREF=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/thunderbird/addon/875\" TARGET=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/thunderbird/addon/875</a><br />\n　　下载 <a HREF=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/thunderbird/downloads/file/4287/tb_header_tools_extension-0.4.5-tb.xpi\" TARGET=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/thunderbir&#8230;on-0.4.5-tb.xpi</a><br />\n　　安装 略<br />\n　　应用 右键点击邮件，弹出菜单上“change header details”<br />\n　　<img CLASS=\"linked-image\" SRC=\"http://img201.imageshack.us/img201/8445/0411003es1.png\" BORDER=\"0\"><br />\n<b>问题</b><br />\n　　若原标题无中文，则不能直接加入汉字<br />\n<b>原因</b><br />\n　　编码问题<br />\n　　查看源文件可知，英文标题形如 Subject: CIO Insider: Stress<br />\nTolerance<br />\n　　而中文标题则形如 Subject:<br />\n=?gb2312?B?U0FQvczT/cXg0bW087vh?=<br />\n　　或 Subject: =?x-gbk?Q?=CE=D2=CA=C7=B1=EA=CC=E2?=<br />\n<b>解决</b><br />\n　　先编辑源文件(Edit Full Source)，把标题（Subject:）处改为“<br />\n=?GB2312?B?19Y=?=”形式（可从其他mail源文件中复制）<br />\n　　然后，就可以直接输入中文了。<br />\n<b>结论</b><br />\n　　Thunderbird确有不足（很多客户端可直接改），但加上扩展，基本能克服\n</div>\n<p>※初稿07年4月;出自<font COLOR=\"#FF0000\">善用<font COLOR=\"#009900\">佳软</font></font><a HREF=\"http://xbeta.info/\" TARGET=\"_blank\">xbeta.info</a><br />\n※作者xbeta;采用CC创作共用协议,可保留本信息并&lt;<a HREF=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/u/46dac66f010002fq\" TARGET=\"_blank\">署名、非商业和保持一致</a>&gt;转载<br />\n></iframe></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Thunderbird或许不是最好的免费邮件客户端，但xbeta坚守之，并总结技巧。 需求 　　收到标题为空的 [&hellip;]</p>\n","protected":false},"author":15,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":["旧.网络相关","未分类"],"tags":["all"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/236"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/users/15"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/comments?post=236"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/236/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=236"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/categories?post=236"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/tags?post=236"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]},"wp_type":"post"}